== English ==
=== Etymology ===
{{blend|scientific|fiction}}, coined by science fiction [[w:pulp magazine|pulp magazine]] editor [[w:Hugo Gernsback|Hugo Gernsback]] in 1926

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun-unc}}

#[[science fiction|Science fiction]].

====Usage notes====
*'''Scientifiction''' was proposed by as a name for this genre in 1926 but was superseded by '''science fiction'''; the term is now only seen in early science fiction magazines and [[fandom]].

====Synonyms====
*[[science fiction]]
*[[sci-fi]]
*[[SF]]

